hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: What's your number? servimedical ips To try to get that sense of control, I recommend something low-tech. Take a little spiral notebook that a woman can put in her purse or a man can put in his pocket, and every time you spend any money over the course of either a paycheck cycle or a whole month, write down everything you spend money on. The debit card has become the enemy of the person who doesn't know where their money goes. Without thinking about it, they slide it here, they slide it there, and before you know it, the dollars add up to be meaningful money over the course of a month.
